thread.title: John C. Pharris
thread.title_full: Carid reviewed by John C. Pharris

author: John C. Pharris
title: John C. Pharris
text: Wanted to upgrade to a CAI; Volant was the choice since I have a functional ram air scoop on the hood now. With the Volant, the ram air is perfect with the ability to remove the lid. Kristy was great in insuring that I got what I wanted at the right price! Great experience and will be buying from them again.
